The song and Artist: http://youtu.be/XTUaPbIaz4c (see his links)

I loved the song so much I wanted it in my game. No, it\'s not the Skyrim theme dubstepified, but more closely related to Oblivion, however, I still find it very fitting and well done.

Mod in action: http://youtu.be/yPVC0MdgUv4 (thanks for this Pascual!)

Please support the artist if you enjoy the tune!
